  RFC2530 [label="RFC2530
Indicating Supported Media Features
Using Extensions to DSN and MDN
1999", shape=ellipse, URL="RFC2530.html", target="_top", tooltip="This memo describes a format for generating Message Disposition Notifications and Delivery Status Notifications which contain such information. [STANDARDS-TRACK]"];
